{"id":471,"date":"2021-02-07T12:24:14","date_gmt":"2021-02-07T12:24:14","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/dev.demowebcloud.com\/?page_id=471"},"modified":"2021-09-21T20:04:34","modified_gmt":"2021-09-21T20:04:34","slug":"announcement","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/nacom.org\/announcement\/","title":{"rendered":"Announcement"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-215793 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-587013 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-233517 list-post-type list-post category \">\t\t<div class=\"list-item post-1\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"post-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/figure>\n\t\t\t\t<h3><a href=\"https:\/\/nacom.org\/news-1\/\">Inception Workshop on Intended Nationally Determined Contributions (INDC)<\/a><\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"kc-entry_meta\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text\">\n\t\t\t\t\tThe Ministry of Environment and Forests held an Inception Workshop on Intended Nationally Determined Contributions (INDC) on Sunday, the 25th\u00a0of January, 2015 at the Surma Conference Hall of the Pan\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"kc-read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/nacom.org\/news-1\/\">Read more<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-124341 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-884246 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-407986 kc-raw-code\"><div class=\"kc_text_block \">\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span>Job Advertisement<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Nature Conservation Management (NACOM) is looking for 16 (Sixteen) Community Organizers to implement Elephant Conservation &amp; Human Elephant Conflict Resolution (RFP Package NO: SD-40) project. Interested candidates are encouraged to apply for the position. <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Name of the position: <\/span><\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Community Organizers.&nbsp;&nbsp; <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <br>\r\n\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Duty Station: <\/span><\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Dhaka, Chattogram, Cox&rsquo;s Bazar, Mymensingh, and Sherpur.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <br>\r\n\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Requirements:<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Minimum: HSC <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Experience in Community Mobilization, Awareness Raising is preferable.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Preference will be given to candidates are living in Dhaka, Chattogram, Cox&rsquo;s Bazar, Mymensingh, and Sherpur and <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Candidates having knowledge on elephant movement and human-elephant conflicts will be given preference<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Previous working experience with the forest department will be an asset;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Must be a smartphone user. <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n  <\/ul>\r\n\r\n  <br>\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span>Responsibilities:<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Organize training, meeting, awareness campaign on elephant conservation;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Work with the forest department and Elephant Response Team (ERT) to protect Elephant;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Coordinate with the ERTs and facilitate Bi-monthly meeting;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Assist Team leader and Wildlife expert in the field;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Provide support in organizing World Elephant Day;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Ability to work under pressure and to deal with challenging situations;<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Any other task assigned by management.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n  <\/ul>\r\n  <br>\r\n\r\n  <p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Gross Salary: <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">15000 BDT per month (Gross Salary). <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <br>\r\n\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Apply<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Please submit your CV and Photograph (Max. size 300 KB) for the advertised post to <\/span><\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"mailto:hr.nacom@gmail.com\"><strong><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">hr.nacom@gmail.com<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/a><\/span><strong> <\/strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">no later than September 27, 2021 (5:30 pm Bangladesh Standard Time).<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <br>\r\n\r\n  <p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Please Note<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Only the short-listed candidates will be called for an interview<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">No TA\/DA is permissible for attending the written test\/interview<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">Female candidates are highly encouraged to apply<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n    <li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span><span style=\"color:#222222\">NACOM reserve the rights to cancel part of this advertisement or the entire advertisement without any clarification\/notice. <\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/li>\r\n  <\/ol>\r\n  <p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_sta